Class CompoundTagFormula

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.core.vo.query.logical.LogicalTagFormula
      • com.communote.server.core.vo.query.logical.CompoundTagFormula

  • public class CompoundTagFormula
extends LogicalTagFormula
    An logical tag formula that can contain atoms and other compound formulas. The sub elements are connected by logical disjunction or conjunction.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
